<article articleID="LBmn_00005_F001">
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><sampling type="start" /><ruby rubyText="ば">芭</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「これは<ruby rubyText="おどろ">驚</ruby>いた。</sentence>
<sentence><ruby rubyText="な">菜</ruby><ruby rubyText="え">エ</ruby><ruby rubyText="もん">門</ruby>さんがそんな<ruby rubyText="ゆう">優</ruby><ruby rubyText="が">雅</ruby>な<ruby rubyText="き">季</ruby><ruby rubyText="ご">語</ruby>を<ruby rubyText="し">知</ruby>っていたとは。</sentence>
<sentence>で、その<ruby rubyText="あと">後</ruby>は？」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="わ">話</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「うん、『<ruby rubyText="はる">春</ruby><ruby rubyText="さめ">雨</ruby>やのどにツルツル<ruby rubyText="た">食</ruby>べやすい』」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="ば">芭</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「トホホ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="わ">話</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「あとねえ、『<ruby rubyText="つき">月</ruby>に<ruby rubyText="くも">雲</ruby>…』」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="ば">芭</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ほう、<ruby rubyText="こん">今</ruby><ruby rubyText="ど">度</ruby>は<ruby rubyText="よ">良</ruby>さそうじゃな」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="わ">話</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「うん、『<ruby rubyText="つき">月</ruby>に<ruby rubyText="くも">雲</ruby><ruby rubyText="たま">玉</ruby><ruby rubyText="ご">子</ruby>に<ruby rubyText="のり">海苔</ruby>をかけたよう』」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="ば">芭</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「トホホ、やっぱりそんなのか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="わ">話</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「それから『<ruby rubyText="はる">春</ruby>の<ruby rubyText="うみ">海</ruby><ruby rubyText="すな">砂</ruby>が<ruby rubyText="く">食</ruby>えたら<ruby rubyText="おお">大</ruby>もうけ』とか『<ruby rubyText="くさ">草</ruby><ruby rubyText="もち">餅</ruby>を<ruby rubyText="となり">隣</ruby>の<ruby rubyText="ひと">人</ruby>はふたつ<ruby rubyText="た">食</ruby>べ』とか」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="ば">芭</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「なんだか<ruby rubyText="た">食</ruby>べ<ruby rubyText="もの">物</ruby>のことばかりじゃな」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="わ">話</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「だってうちにいた<ruby rubyText="ころ">頃</ruby>、<ruby rubyText="しん">心</ruby><ruby rubyText="ぱい">配</ruby>って<ruby rubyText="い">言</ruby>ったら<ruby rubyText="た">食</ruby>べ<ruby rubyText="もの">物</ruby>のことしかなかったもん。</sentence>
<sentence>じいちゃんもばあちゃんも、<ruby rubyText="あさ">朝</ruby>ごはんを<ruby rubyText="た">食</ruby>べ<ruby rubyText="お">終</ruby>わると<ruby rubyText="ばん">晩</ruby>に<ruby rubyText="た">食</ruby>べる<ruby rubyText="もの">物</ruby>がないけどどうしようって<ruby rubyText="しん">心</ruby><ruby rubyText="ぱい">配</ruby>して、<ruby rubyText="ばん">晩</ruby>ごはんを<ruby rubyText="た">食</ruby>べ<ruby rubyText="お">終</ruby>わると<ruby rubyText="あす">明日</ruby>の<ruby rubyText="あさ">朝</ruby>に<ruby rubyText="た">食</ruby>べる<ruby rubyText="もの">物</ruby>がないけどどうしようって<ruby rubyText="しん">心</ruby><ruby rubyText="ぱい">配</ruby>してた。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">でもその<ruby rubyText="ほか">他</ruby>にはなんの<ruby rubyText="しん">心</ruby><ruby rubyText="ぱい">配</ruby>もなくって<ruby rubyText="まい">毎</ruby><ruby rubyText="にち">日</ruby><ruby rubyText="たの">楽</ruby>しかったなあ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="ば">芭</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ううむ、どうにもノーテンキな<ruby rubyText="いっ">一</ruby><ruby rubyText="か">家</ruby>じゃの、ハハハ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">でも、どうじゃ、<ruby rubyText="わ">話</ruby><ruby rubyText="きち">吉</ruby>も<ruby rubyText="はい">俳</ruby><ruby rubyText="く">句</ruby>をつくってみては」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="わ">話</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「お<ruby rubyText="し">師</ruby><ruby rubyText="しょう">匠</ruby><ruby rubyText="さま">様</ruby>、<ruby rubyText="おし">教</ruby>えてくれる？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="ば">芭</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「おお、もちろんだとも」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="わ">話</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「なら、なんか<ruby rubyText="う">浮</ruby>かんだら<ruby rubyText="い">言</ruby>うよ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="ば">芭</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「よしよし、<ruby rubyText="たの">楽</ruby>しみにしているぞ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　さて、そんな<ruby rubyText="はなし">話</ruby>で<ruby rubyText="も">盛</ruby>りあがっているうちに<ruby rubyText="みち">道</ruby>は<ruby rubyText="に">二</ruby><ruby rubyText="ほん">本</ruby><ruby rubyText="まつ">松</ruby>の<ruby rubyText="やど">宿</ruby>に<ruby rubyText="はい">入</ruby>ってきました。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　もう<ruby rubyText="ゆう">夕</ruby><ruby rubyText="がた">方</ruby>に<ruby rubyText="ちか">近</ruby>く、<ruby rubyText="やど">宿</ruby>を<ruby rubyText="と">取</ruby>ってもいいのですが、ふたりともまだ<ruby rubyText="げん">元</ruby><ruby rubyText="き">気</ruby>なので<ruby rubyText="あ">安</ruby><ruby rubyText="だち">達</ruby><ruby rubyText="が">ヶ</ruby><ruby rubyText="はら">原</ruby>まで<ruby rubyText="あし">足</ruby>を<ruby rubyText="の">伸</ruby>ばそうということになりました。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<rejectedBlock type="old" />
<sentence>と、<ruby rubyText="こ">古</ruby><ruby rubyText="か">歌</ruby>にもうたわれるとおり、<ruby rubyText="あ">安</ruby><ruby rubyText="だち">達</ruby><ruby rubyText="が">ヶ</ruby><ruby rubyText="はら">原</ruby>にはその<ruby rubyText="むかし">昔</ruby>、<ruby rubyText="ひと">人</ruby>を<ruby rubyText="ころ">殺</ruby>してその<ruby rubyText="にく">肉</ruby>を<ruby rubyText="た">食</ruby>べる<ruby rubyText="おに">鬼</ruby><ruby rubyText="ばば">婆</ruby>がいたという<ruby rubyText="でん">伝</ruby><ruby rubyText="せつ">説</ruby>があります。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
<paragraph>
<sentence>　その<ruby rubyText="おに">鬼</ruby><ruby rubyText="ばば">婆</ruby>が<ruby rubyText="す">住</ruby>んでいたという<ruby rubyText="いわ">岩</ruby><ruby rubyText="や">屋</ruby>が<ruby rubyText="のこ">残</ruby>っているので<ruby rubyText="み">見</ruby>に<ruby rubyText="い">行</ruby>こうというのです。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　<ruby rubyText="ほん">本</ruby><ruby rubyText="かい">街</ruby><ruby rubyText="どう">道</ruby>をはずれて<ruby rubyText="きゅう">急</ruby>に<ruby rubyText="ひと">人</ruby><ruby rubyText="どお">通</ruby>りの<ruby rubyText="へ">減</ruby>ったいなか<ruby rubyText="みち">道</ruby>を<ruby rubyText="ある">歩</ruby>きながら<ruby rubyText="わ">話</ruby><ruby rubyText="きち">吉</ruby>がたずねました。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="わ">話</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ねえ、お<ruby rubyText="し">師</ruby><ruby rubyText="しょう">匠</ruby><ruby rubyText="さま">様</ruby>。</sentence>
<sentence>その<ruby rubyText="おに">鬼</ruby><ruby rubyText="ばば">婆</ruby>の<ruby rubyText="はなし">話</ruby>、<ruby rubyText="き">聞</ruby>きたい！</sentence>
<sentence>　<ruby rubyText="き">聞</ruby>きたい！」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="ば">芭</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ふむ、どうせそうくるだろうと<ruby rubyText="おも">思</ruby>っていた。</sentence>
<sentence>よしよし、もうこのあたりは<ruby rubyText="あ">安</ruby><ruby rubyText="だち">達</ruby><ruby rubyText="が">ヶ</ruby><ruby rubyText="はら">原</ruby>らしい。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">あそこに<ruby rubyText="ちゃ">茶</ruby><ruby rubyText="みせ">店</ruby>があるから<ruby rubyText="もち">餅</ruby>でも<ruby rubyText="た">食</ruby>べながら<ruby rubyText="はな">話</ruby>してあげよう」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ふたりは<ruby rubyText="みち">道</ruby>ぞいの<ruby rubyText="ふる">古</ruby>ぼけた<ruby rubyText="ちゃ">茶</ruby><ruby rubyText="みせ">店</ruby>の、<ruby rubyText="うす">薄</ruby><ruby rubyText="よご">汚</ruby>れた<ruby rubyText="えん">縁</ruby><ruby rubyText="だい">台</ruby>に<ruby rubyText="こし">腰</ruby>をかけました。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　お<ruby rubyText="きゃく">客</ruby>が<ruby rubyText="ぜん">全</ruby><ruby rubyText="ぜん">然</ruby><ruby rubyText="こ">来</ruby>ないらしくて<ruby rubyText="みせ">店</ruby>をしまいかけていたおばあさんが、あわてて<ruby rubyText="ちゃ">茶</ruby>を<ruby rubyText="も">持</ruby>って<ruby rubyText="で">出</ruby>てきました。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="ば">芭</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「こんにちは。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">のぼりに<ruby rubyText="か">書</ruby>いてある『<ruby rubyText="めい">名</ruby><ruby rubyText="ぶつ">物</ruby><ruby rubyText="おに">鬼</ruby><ruby rubyText="ばば">婆</ruby><ruby rubyText="もち">餅</ruby>』というのを<ruby rubyText="ふた">二</ruby><ruby rubyText="さら">皿</ruby>いただきましょう」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ば</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「おや、ありがとうございます。</sentence>
<sentence><ruby rubyText="おに">鬼</ruby><ruby rubyText="ばば">婆</ruby><ruby rubyText="もち">餅</ruby>は<ruby rubyText="ひ">火</ruby>あぶりと<ruby rubyText="ど">土</ruby><ruby rubyText="ざ">左</ruby><ruby rubyText="え">衛</ruby><ruby rubyText="もん">門</ruby>のどちらがよろしゅうございますか？」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="ば">芭</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「はあ？」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ば</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「ホホホ、<ruby rubyText="ひ">火</ruby>あぶりは<ruby rubyText="や">焼</ruby>くこと、<ruby rubyText="ど">土</ruby><ruby rubyText="ざ">左</ruby><ruby rubyText="え">衛</ruby><ruby rubyText="もん">門</ruby>は<ruby rubyText="に">煮</ruby>ることでございますよ」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="ば">芭</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「ああ、<ruby rubyText="おどろ">驚</ruby>いた。</sentence>
<sentence><ruby rubyText="なにわ">難波</ruby>の<ruby rubyText="あし">芦</ruby>は<ruby rubyText="い">伊</ruby><ruby rubyText="せ">勢</ruby>の<ruby rubyText="はま">浜</ruby><ruby rubyText="おぎ">荻</ruby>とか、ところが<ruby rubyText="か">変</ruby>われば<ruby rubyText="よ">呼</ruby>び<ruby rubyText="な">名</ruby>も<ruby rubyText="か">変</ruby>わる。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">ではわたしは<ruby rubyText="ひ">火</ruby>あぶりでお<ruby rubyText="ねが">願</ruby>いしましょう」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ば</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「はい。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="いま">今</ruby>、お<ruby rubyText="も">持</ruby>ちしますので、そこの<ruby rubyText="ひ">火</ruby><ruby rubyText="ばち">鉢</ruby>でご<ruby rubyText="じ">自</ruby><ruby rubyText="ぶん">分</ruby>で<ruby rubyText="や">焼</ruby>いてお<ruby rubyText="め">召</ruby>し<ruby rubyText="あ">上</ruby>がりください」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi"><ruby rubyText="わ">話</ruby></sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi">　「おらは<ruby rubyText="ど">土</ruby><ruby rubyText="ざ">左</ruby><ruby rubyText="え">衛</ruby><ruby rubyText="もん">門</ruby>ね」</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">ば</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence type="quasi"><sentence>　「はい。</sentence>
<sentence><ruby rubyText="しょう">少</ruby><ruby rubyText="しょう">々</ruby>お<ruby rubyText="ま">待</ruby>ちを。</sentence>
<sentence>この<ruby rubyText="い">言</ruby>いかた、おもしろいでしょ？</sentence>
<sentence>　やっぱりこれからの<ruby rubyText="しょう">商</ruby><ruby rubyText="ばい">売</ruby>は<ruby rubyText="わ">話</ruby><ruby rubyText="だい">題</ruby><ruby rubyText="せい">性</ruby>が<ruby rubyText="だい">大</ruby><ruby rubyText="じ">事</ruby>ですか<sampling type="end" />らね、<ruby rubyText="じ">地</ruby><ruby rubyText="もと">元</ruby>の<ruby rubyText="かわら">瓦</ruby><ruby rubyText="ばん">版</ruby>にも<ruby rubyText="と">取</ruby>りあげられたんですよ。</sentence>
<sentence type="quasi">そのわりにはお<ruby rubyText="きゃく">客</ruby>さんが<ruby rubyText="き">来</ruby>てくれないんですけどね、ホホホ」</sentence>
</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
</article>
